IMAPAccount work
Host localhost
Port 1143
User %USERNAME%
PassCmd "pass `cat ~/.mutt_work`"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType None
Timeout 300

IMAPStore work-remote
Account work

MaildirStore work-local
Path ~/mail/work/
Inbox ~/mail/work/Inbox

Channel work-main
Master :work-remote:
Slave :work-local:
Patterns "Archive" "Important" "Drafts"
Create Both
Remove Both
Expunge Both
Sync All
SyncState *
CopyArrivalDate yes

Channel work-junk
Master :work-remote:Junk
Slave :work-local:Junk
Create Both
Remove Both
Expunge Both
Sync All
SyncState *
CopyArrivalDate yes
MaxMessages 50

Channel work-inbox
Master :work-remote:INBOX
Slave :work-local:Inbox
Create Both
Remove Both
Expunge Both
Sync All
SyncState *
CopyArrivalDate yes
MaxMessages 500

Channel work-nn
Master :work-remote:NN
Slave :work-local:NN
Create Both
Remove Both
Expunge Both
Sync All
SyncState *
CopyArrivalDate yes
MaxMessages 200

Channel work-devops
Master :work-remote:DevOps
Slave :work-local:DevOps
Create Both
Remove Both
Expunge Both
Sync All
SyncState *
CopyArrivalDate yes
MaxMessages 1000

Channel work-low
Master :work-remote:LowPriority
Slave :work-local:LowPriority
Create Both
Remove Both
Expunge Both
Sync All
SyncState *
CopyArrivalDate yes
MaxMessages 100
ExpireUnread yes

Channel work-service
Master :work-remote:Service
Slave :work-local:Service
Create Both
Remove Both
Expunge Both
Sync All
SyncState *
CopyArrivalDate yes
MaxMessages 100
ExpireUnread yes

Channel work-trash
Master :work-remote:"Deleted Items"
Slave :work-local:Trash
Create Both
Remove Both
Expunge Both
Sync All
SyncState *
CopyArrivalDate yes
MaxMessages 100
ExpireUnread yes

Channel work-sent
Master :work-remote:"Sent Items"
Slave :work-local:Sent
Create Both
Remove Both
Expunge Both
Sync All
SyncState *
CopyArrivalDate yes
MaxMessages 100

Group work
Channel work-inbox
Channel work-main
Channel work-junk
Channel work-nn
Channel work-devops
Channel work-low
Channel work-trash
Channel work-sent
Channel work-service
